TITLE: Data Mode Switching (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript snippet shows how to switch between binding mode and value mode in the `FWorkbook` using the `sheets-source-binding` plugin. This determines whether the cell displays the bound path or the actual data value from the source.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dream-num/univer/blob/dev/packages-experimental/sheets-source-binding/README.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// Binding mode
fWorkbook.usePathMode();
// Value mode
fWorkbook.useValueMode()
```

