TITLE: Registering the Sheets Filter UI Plugin in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Imports the necessary CSS and registers both the UniverSheetsFilterPlugin (from @univerjs/sheets-filter) and the UniverSheetsFilterUIPlugin (from @univerjs/sheets-filter-ui) with a Univer instance. This enables the filtering functionality and its corresponding user interface.
